Not wasting any time, Scatterblaster powers up his boosters and launches into 
the air, barely avoiding Wespah's shots.  "So that's how you wanna play, eh?  
Alright then..." he said as he brought his rifle to bear down towards Wespah, 
twenty explosive bullets launching out towards Scatterblaster's opponent.
